Individuals / organizations are honoured with various awards such as Dr. Punjabrao Deshmukh Krishi Ratna Award, Vasantrao Naik Krishi Bhushan Award, Jijamata Krishi Bhushan Award, Krishi Bhushan (Organic Farming) Award, Vasantrao Naik Krishi Mitra Award, Yuva Shetkari Award, Udyan Pandit Award, Vasantrao Naik Krishi Nishtha Shetkari Award (General Group / Tribal Group), Padma Shri Dr. Vithalrao Vikhe Patil Krishi Sevaratna Award (Commissionerate / Ministry level). Accordingly, it was under consideration of the Government to honour farmers / institutions by conferring various Krishi Awards for the year 2020, 2021 and 2022.
Names of Awardees for presentation of Agriculture Awards for the year 2020, 2021 and 2022

In order to determine. The meeting chaired by the Minister (Agriculture) has finalised the names of individuals / institutions as mentioned in the attached Year-wise Statement-2020, Statement-2021 and Statement-2022 for the Krishi Awards for the year 2020, 2021 and 2022 and the Government hereby approves conferment and conferment of the awards.
Government Decision Number: Award-2024 / Q. 05/4 - A, D. 23.02.2024
Awards to individuals / organizations selected for various agricultural awards under this.
The Commissioner (Agriculture) is responsible for organizing the award distribution program for distribution.
